<br>
I've never been obsessed with money.  I never ask for more gems than is necessary to cover my costs, I try to make sure that some of the gems get to the enchanter if Rune is being used, and I never accept payment for a rez.  However, I know that a lot of clerics have a different perspective, and I can't say that they're unjustified.  Clerics <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> do</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> get screwed on periodot costs a lot.  There just isn't an easy answer to this issue, other than simply avoiding pickup groups. <p>Sagemon Prayeth<BR>
