<br>
Puller, and any pure caster , and usually the shaman if they're there for slowing, get symboled. And those symbols get refreshed instantly when it drops and they request it. I don't even symbol myself. I'd like to think I'm a good cleric, I do more than my fair share and people typically don't die with me around. Believe it or not, people generally understand why you don't symbol a secondary tank, or anyone else who never seems to get hit. Of course things will change when I get group aego in oh, 2 gold. <br>
